title: Jason Welsher from To Die For Clothing
itunes:title: Jason Welsher from To Die For Clothing
description:
I had the pleasure of speaking with one of my oldest friends Jason Welsher, from street wear/graffiti art clothing company To Die For, about his musical beginnings, his most important lessons learned and how difficult it is to maintain a small business.
